snippet.title: Moonbirds x Nifty Island
snippet.description:
Nifty Island and Moonbirds are partnering to bring the best art collecting community in web3 to the world of games.

Moonbird avatars and nft prizes will be available for holders in our soon to be released open beta.

A new beginning for NFTs is coming. Don't miss it!

Announcement: https://x.com/Nifty_Island/status/1719031616150884581

Follow the Project 🏝️
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Nifty_Island
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/nifty_island/
TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@nifty_island?lang=en

BRING YOUR NFTS TO LIFE!
